VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)(secret_key_base|secret|apikey|token|password)\s*[:=]\s*[\'\"][^\'\"]{8,}[\'\"]
WHEN EXPR MISSING:example|sample|dummy|test|placeholder
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects likely hardcoded secret material.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Sinatra Hardcoded Secret Material.
